t=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bor=
der-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: s=
olid; background-color: #ccc;"> This blew my mind</a>:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Musk told the jury that the propos=
ed $420 per share price to take Tesla private was, =E2=80=9Cnot a joke,=E2=
=80=9D and said any connections between it and references to marijuana trop=
es were purely a coincidence.=C2=A0</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">What. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbu=
siness.com/click/30347296.266447/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueWFob28uY29tL25vdy9lbG9uLW=
11c2staW5zaXN0cy1pbmZhbW91cy00MjAtMTk1NDIzODczLmh0bWw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a=
23cBa11bdcd5" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_bla=
nk" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-botto=
m-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; bac=
kground-color: #ccc;"> And</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Musk acknowledged that the actual Tesla stock =
price after adding a 20% premium totaled $419 and more than 50 cents, and e=
xplained that he rounded the number up to $420. It was "a coincidence," he =
said. Pressed by the plaintiff's lawyer about whether he believed his "girl=
friend"=E2=80=94presumably the famous DJ Claire Elise Boucher, otherwise kn=
own as Grimes, with whom Musk has two children=E2=80=94"would find it funny=
," Musk said he wasn't sure.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">"I don't know if she found it funny or not. Bu=
t the 420 price was not a joke," Musk said.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">"There is some karma around 420," Musk noted m=
oments later, "although I should question if that is good or bad karma at t=
his point.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">What. What. Look, again, my assumption was alw=
ays that the SEC has a videotape of Musk saying it was a weed joke. Perhaps=
 I am wrong. But what if I=E2=80=99m right! If you are a plaintiffs=E2=80=
=99=C2=A0lawyer in this case, you had better be calling the SEC for that vi=
deotape. If you are the SEC =E2=80=94=C2=A0and the SEC has taken a lot of a=
buse from Musk in recent years and wouldn=E2=80=99t mind sticking it to him=
 a bit=C2=A0=E2=80=94=C2=A0you had better be calling the plaintiffs=E2=80=
=99 lawyers and offering it to them. Frankly if you are the SEC you ought t=
o clip that videotape and email it to me to publish in this newsletter! Hon=
estly what is this newsletter for if not to litigate whether Elon Musk=E2=
=80=99s habit of buying, or <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.=
com/click/30347296.266447/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2Fyd=
GljbGVzLzIwMjItMDctMDkvZWxvbi1zLW91dD9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMTI0MjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1=
dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzAxMjQmdXR=
tX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB046d7153" itemprop=3D=
"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0000=
00; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bott=
om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  p=
retending to buy</a>, companies for prices that involve the number =E2=80=
=9C420=E2=80=9D is a weed joke?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">By the way, I=E2=80=99ve <a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30347296.266447/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21=
iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMDktMjgvbXVzay1zLXRlc2xhLWZ1bi1kb2=
VzLW5vdC1hbXVzZS1zZWM_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDEyNDIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lb=
WFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwMTI0JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1t=
b25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cC0e9fbe12" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" item=
scope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decorat=
ion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00000=
0; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  said this before<=
/a>, but as a price $420 seems totally reasonable (and frankly cheap given =
Tesla=E2=80=99s subsequent performance<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#=
footnote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: no=
ne !important; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-bl=
ock;">
<span>[1]</span>
</a>), and Musk=E2=80=99s process of taking the closing price, adding 20%, =
and rounding to a pleasing number is just fine. If I were on the jury, my d=
ecision about whether or not Musk did securities fraud would not really be =
affected by whether the price was a weed joke. But as a citizen and a finan=
cial columnist, I need to know whether it was a weed joke.</p>
